Little bit of background info: This was our big Europe adventure that took place in 2015. We spent two weeks traveling around the three different countries of England, Ireland, and Spain. The specific cities I have names were the ones that we stayed in and spent to most time in. We had an unforgetable time, and if you are looking to have a European adventure of your own definitley take notes and feel free to ask questions by sending us an email. We appreciate you taking the time to explore our website! Bon Voyage!
